Node "Cath_1a_2c_1"
notes "First impressions count.\nDecrement the local variable Cath_Mood by 5.\nIncrement the local variable Cath_Alex_Daught by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I see. Like that, is it? Well, I'm Catherine, and in case you get any funny ideas, that makes me Alexander's daughter. The same Alexander that runs Sandover."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for the General Atomics International base. Do you know where I can find it?" linkto "Cath_2a_1"  notes "This option only appears if the PC has accepted the 'Find the GAI base' quest from whomever gives it out at V31.\nIf Alexander has died from depression (see the wiki for details) go to Cath_2b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You don't seem as sick as the other people in Sandover. Why is that?" linkto "Cath_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to speak to Alexander. Where can I find him?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about your father?" linkto "Cath_1a_2c_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I look for find Gen'rul Tomacks Nun-nash-nall base. You know?" linkto "Cath_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why you not ill like rest of cave people?" linkto "Cath_3_1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me where find Alexrunder-run-Sunduvver." linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[LEAVE]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
