Node "Cath_2b_1"
notes "The Cath_2b_* path is where the PC finds out what Catherine knows about the GAI base. (Precious little). It is used in place of Cath_2a_* if Alexander is dead."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[She screws her eyes in thought and silently repeats the name to herself.] Nope. Name doesn't ring a bell. [She sighs.] My father might have known... but..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
