Node "Cath_3_3c_1"
notes "Increment the local variable Cath_Alex_Daught by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "He's the leader of Sandover. If you haven't spoken to him yourself, yet, go and introduce yourself. He's just over there. [She points to the smartly robed figure on the southern side of the room.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "So his daughter gets enough medicine whilst the rest of the town goes without. Very convenient." linkto "Cath_3_3c_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you a question about something else." linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll do that now. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_3_3c_2"
notes "She didn't like that!\nDecrement the local variable Cath_Mood by 5."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Listen, pal, it's not an abuse of his position. He pays for our meds out of his own pocket, okay? Same as everyone else in Sandover."
 NPCFemaleText "Listen, lady, it's not an abuse of his position. He pays for our meds out of his own pocket, okay? Same as everyone else in Sandover."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you a question about something else." linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whatever helps you sleep at night. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_1"
notes "The Cath_4_* path is where the PC can find out what Catherine does around Sandover, and that she helps Alexander with decision-making."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Being the town leader's daughter isn't all plain sailing. It means I have - ugh - responsibilities."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What sorts of responsibilities are those?" linkto "Cath_4_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2a" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Cath_Alex_Daught == 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, of course, I'm never allowed to have any fun. \"We're in a position of authority, Catherine, we have to be seen to be respectable.\" [She rolls her eyes.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Aside from having to act the part, what does being the leader's daughter mean you have to do?" linkto "Cath_4_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "You've got it easy compared to everyone else in these caves, believe me." linkto "Cath_4_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "Sounds like it could get tiresome." linkto "Cath_4_3c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Cath_Alex_Daught == 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_3a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Oh, there's usually errands to be run, or whatever. You know, \"take this piece of paper to so-and-so, Catherine. Find out when such-and-such is happening from what's-his-name, Catherine.\""
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Cath_4_3a_2"  notes ""
