Node "Cath_4_3a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "But sometimes Dad will want someone he can trust to talk to about the big things Sandover has to deal with. Things he has trouble making decisions about."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Can he trust you?" linkto "Cath_4_3a_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What kinds of big decisions are those?" linkto "Cath_4_3a_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Cath_Alex_Daught == 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_3a_3a"
notes "She does not like her trustworthiness being brought into question!\nDecrement the local variable Cath_Mood by 5."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Of course he can trust me! I might not love being the leader's daughter all the time, but he's still my Dad."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What kinds of big decisions have you helped your father with?" linkto "Cath_4_3a_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Cath_Alex_Daught == 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_3a_3b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Okay, one example. There was this gang that used to live in the caves that called themselves The Vultures. They kind of made a real nuisance of themselves - partying all night long, the occasional fight, never doing any work, that sort of thing."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Cath_4_3a_3b_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_3a_3b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "So, Dad asked Saman to get rid of them - you know, throw them out of the caves. But Saman was all like, \"No problem, I can have them dead by tomorrow morning.\" He thought the best way of getting rid of them was to kill them all, so they wouldn't come back to cause trouble."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Cath_4_3a_3b_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_3a_3b_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Dad didn't know which was best, though. Throw them out of the caves and risk them coming back angrier than ever, or kill them outright? So he asked me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What did you say?" linkto "Cath_4_3a_3b_4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_4_3a_3b_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hell, there was no way I wanted a bloodbath in Sandover! I told him to make sure Saman cooled his heels and *only* evict the Vultures from the caves. Good thing I did, because that's exactly what happened."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You obviously have a lot of influence upon your father, then." linkto "Cath_4_3a_3b_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is your father?" linkto "Cath_2a_2a" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Cath_Alex_Daught == 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
