Node "Cath_5_1a_1"
notes "The Cath_5_* path is where the PC can try to persuade Catherine to either side of the euthanasia debate."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*That* tired old subject? No wonder Dad didn't want you talking about it; he's had people bothering him about banning or legalizing euthanasia since forever."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What is your opinion on the matter?" linkto "Cath_5_1a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else, then." linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It was worth a try. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_5_1a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The 'assisted suicide' thing gets talked about so much that I got sick of thinking about it. One day, someone on the anti-euth team will convince you to their way of thinking; next day, a pro-euther will swing you back again. I guess you could say I'm somewhere in the middle."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've heard the best arguments on the subject. If I can convince you which is the best viewpoint too, would you talk to your father and try to persuade him to change the law?" linkto "Cath_5_1a_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else, then." linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It was worth a try. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Cath_5_1a_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "You really think you've got something I haven't heard before, huh? What the hell, I'll listen. So, which camp are you in - pro-euth or anti-euth?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I support the legalization of euthanasia." linkto "Cath_5_4a_01a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I am in favor of an outright ban on euthanasia." linkto "Cath_5_4b_01a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Cath_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
