          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "[Repeat this to Catherine; appeal to her sense that the people of Sandover are fundamentally moral.]" linkto "Pro_Euth_Speech_5b"  notes "Normal Speech skill check.\nBeing the town's leader's daughter, she's going to want to believe this more.\nNote: for the Speech check, add/subtract the local variable Cath_Mood to the difficulty modifier."
